49
00:04:39,213 --> 00:04:41,113
Ebihara?

50
00:04:43,513 --> 00:04:45,413
Pops!

51
00:04:45,413 --> 00:04:46,913
You weren't at the usual shop,

52
00:04:46,913 --> 00:04:48,313
