57
00:04:56,113 --> 00:04:58,713
Yes, sir.

58
00:04:58,713 --> 00:05:00,113
-Pops. -Hey! Conan.

59
00:05:00,113 --> 00:05:02,113
Children out...

60
00:05:02,113 --> 00:05:03,213
This is...

61
00:05:05,713 --> 00:05:06,813
Hey.

62
00:05:10,013 --> 00:05:12,613
Okay. I'm going to fly this one more time.

63
00:05:12,613 --> 00:05:14,213
Hey, Genta!

64
00:05:14,213 --> 00:05:15,713
Conan.

65
00:05:15,713 --> 00:05:18,013
Didn't anyone come out of here?

66
00:05:18,013 --> 00:05:20,513
Nobody came out!

67
00:05:20,513 --> 00:05:22,613
Is anything wrong?

68
00:05:24,713 --> 00:05:26,913
